column2: SELECT TOP #    m.dr7objid AS dr7objid_gz, m.ra AS ra_gz, m.dec AS dec_gz,    o.objid AS dr7objid_sdss, o.ra AS ra_sdss, o.dec AS dec_sdss, o.petroMag_g,o.petroMag_r into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.gz2_locations AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
